     *
     * <p>
     * Decision logic:
     * <ul>
     *   <li>If priority allocation disabled: {@link Decision#ALWAYS}</li>
     *   <li>If shard priority below threshold: {@link Decision#ALWAYS}</li>
     *   <li>If node tier matches priority tier: {@link Decision#YES}</li>
     *   <li>If node tier exceeds priority requirement: {@link Decision#YES}</li>
     *   <li>If strict mode and node tier inadequate: {@link Decision#NO}</li>
     *   <li>Otherwise (fallback allowed): {@link Decision#THROTTLE}</li>
     * </ul>
     * </p>
